Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:09.01,Narration,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Long, long ago, when there were \Nfewer stars shining in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:12.38,Narration,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The gods got tired of playing with dice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:17.41,Narration,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,so they created all sorts of beings \Nas well as worlds for them to live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:21.03,Narration,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Humans and elves...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:23.11,Narration,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Dwarves and lizardmen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:27.87,Narration,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They went on adventures \Nwhere they sometimes won,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:29.48,Narration,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but sometimes lost and died...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:33.74,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:36.49,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid. Is this some form of magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:41.97,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to tell the difference \Nbetween mastered technique and magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:44.37,Main,Dwarf Shaman,0000,0000,0000,,You're really saying that in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.78,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,One... two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:53.99,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:55.97,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,They're highly sensitive to smells.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:56.89,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:01:00.47,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the smells of \Nwomen, children, and elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:05.02,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way! Somebody stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:06.94,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,You get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:46.41,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(278,1)}The Strong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:56.21,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... Is this a shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:00.22,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently there was a war \Nhere during the age of gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.18,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,It might be a fortress or something from then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.93,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, it appears to be man-made...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:10.85,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,After the soldiers left, \Nthe goblins called it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.15,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,What a cruel fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.48,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.74,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,This is so gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:21.70,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It does wash off... somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.83,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better remember this when we get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.79,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:31.68,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to being underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.00,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,but somehow being down here just feels wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.76,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's a spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:39.19,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's like a tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.06,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:41.97,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.29,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,An alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.45,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.93,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I spotted it because it's brand new, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:53.64,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Those conniving little goblins...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:55.00,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.28,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:58.25,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any totems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:03.18,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that means there \Naren't any goblin shamans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.58,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it'll be easier for us if \Nthere aren't any spellcasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:11.64,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it seems the absence of shamans \Nis precisely what concerns him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:16.25,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. Ordinary goblins wouldn't \Nbe able to set traps like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.61,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying they have someone leading them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.92,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,We should assume as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:25.18,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that you've destroyed large \Nnests in the past, Sir Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.43,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,How did you do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.77,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke them out, \Nthen crush them individually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:33.26,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Set them on fire, \Ndrown them in the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.35,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,There are many methods,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.49,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,but those won't work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.21,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see their tracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.21,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if we were in a cave, \Nbut on a stone floor like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.32,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.33,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Their hideout is to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.16,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.48,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,The wear on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:54.73,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,They either come from the left \Nand go right, then go back,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.92,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,or they come from the left and go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.48,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Sir Goblin Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.26,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.47,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't the goblins on the left?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:09.93,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... But it'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.11,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,What an awful smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.73,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Breathe through your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.19,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.46,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:32.07,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,The goblins' waste heap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:32.79,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Waste?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.11,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.43,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Goblin Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:52.31,Main,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,...ill... Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:53.77,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,She's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:55.84,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Use a miracle! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:56.60,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:05:59.61,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.07,Main,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.78,Main,Goblin Slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:10.62,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! She's still—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:11.62,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.75,Main,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:23.98,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.50,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're all thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:31.55,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,but I only came here to slay goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:35.31,Main,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:37.83,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:45.62,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,O horns and claws of the father, Iguanodon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:48.50,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,be four limbs and walk upon \Nthis earth with two legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.68,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,A miracle from my ancestors...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.12,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,A dragontooth warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:58.59,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote a letter and explained everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.36,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:07.22,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,My dragontooth warrior should be able to \Ndeliver her to the Elves' Forest safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:09.66,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.30,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.93,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's here, as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.14,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:23.75,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,A map of the ruins. I found it in a rucksack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.61,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,That elf must've been using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:30.49,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,There's a gallery on the left.\NSeems the left was the correct path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.69,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:35.82,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but the more information\Nwe have, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.48,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.00,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.97,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You don't have to say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.03,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:49.81,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get going, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:50.71,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:54.28,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,The goblins must be slain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.87,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,How many spells do we have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:26.46,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I just used Heal, so that leaves two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:29.02,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I have about three,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:31.59,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,but the dragontooth warrior \Nrequires these catalysts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:35.55,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I can only use this spell once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:38.87,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,As for myself... I'd say about four or five.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.64,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.56,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.41,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.56,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overfill your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:50.15,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It'll slow your blood flow, \Ndulling your movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:53.03,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Goblin Slayer! Can't you be more—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.89,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to act tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:57.66,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,If you can come, come. \NIf you can't, head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:58.74,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.30,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.16,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a ranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.75,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to find all the traps \Nand do the scouting if I go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.56,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just make do with those we do have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:13.77,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, you're so... There's no way I can go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.76,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,After what they did to that elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:18.87,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,And my home isn't far from here, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:19.64,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.56,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.81,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, long-ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.85,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't cause a \Ncommotion on enemy ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:33.24,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Dwarves consider goblins \Nmortal enemies, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:38.32,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make them pay for what they did to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:46.92,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I hate taking advice from \Ndwarves, but you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.63,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.34,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're back on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.15,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:16.61,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.18,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,There are quite few.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.55,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.34,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.31,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Goblin Slayer, do you have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.12,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:40.71,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Drink and sing, spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:43.43,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Sing, dance, and sleep like a log!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:46.15,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Show me dreams of fire wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:58.53,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,O merciful Earth Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:02.83,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,grant us the peace to accept all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.74,Main,Goblin Slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Stupor and Silence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:10.93,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,By combining those two spells,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:15.30,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,they'll all fall asleep without making \Na sound or causing a commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:19.34,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,And then the three of us \Nwill slay them, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:45.71,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,They're slick with blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.96,Italics,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I see... He's using their weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:15.21,Italics,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,He... had been doing this all by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.21,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,An ogre!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.65,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,I thought those goblins were awfully quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:00.40,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even make good foot soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:04.60,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,You people aren't like that elf from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.91,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,You dare set foot in our fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:10.81,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... So you're not a goblin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:14.82,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,That's an ogre! An ogre! \NHaven't you heard of them before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:15.63,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.28,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:22.88,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mocking me, the one granted this \Narmy by one of the Demon Lord's generals?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.83,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I knew there were more powerful beings,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:28.47,Main,Gobln slayer,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never heard of you \Nor these Demon Lord generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:38.65,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just have to show \Nyou my power firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:43.35,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Carbunculus... Crescunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.82,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,A fireball's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:46.85,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:49.08,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the size of that thing! \NWhere can we go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:52.55,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,O merciful Earth Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:57.25,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,please protect us, the weak, \Nwith the powers of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.35,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Iacta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.98,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:15.47,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,O... merciful Earth Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:20.19,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,please protect us, the weak, \Nwith the powers of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.40,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:36.36,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:39.33,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.72,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:45.09,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you'll have it \Nas easy as that elf did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:48.10,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Create a dragontooth warrior. \NThere aren't enough of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.30,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, Sir Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:55.07,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,O horns and claws of Father Iguanodon,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:58.07,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,be four limbs and walk upon \Nthis earth with two legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.97,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,O sickle wings of the velociraptor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:09.46,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Slice, fly, and hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:11.24,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I request backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.99,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:15.36,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Time to work, you gnomes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:18.71,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Roll grains of sand together, \Nand it shall become rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.71,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,You measly little dwarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.76,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,You damn dwarves are too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:29.01,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,We have our own way of fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.22,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Stone Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:39.27,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think you could defeat \Nme with that stone magic trick of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.23,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Sir Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:49.36,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Impudent fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.24,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Orcbolg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.79,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:00.75,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mistake me for a mere goblin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:06.14,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,You shall pay dearly for this humiliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.29,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,First, I will shatter your limbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:14.26,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,and make sport of these \Nfemales in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:17.57,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,You shall not have your way, ogre!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:20.85,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Lady Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:24.06,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Goblin Slayer! Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:27.32,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way, you swamp lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.03,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Mage! Lady Ranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.89,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up with that spell, dwarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.26,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:38.37,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,You insolent little insect! \NStop your incessant buzzing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:41.94,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.46,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Stone Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.42,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,You puny insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:55.76,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.40,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... see well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:01.37,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,What's... happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.70,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's still fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.09,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:08.52,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I need a healing potion and a stamina potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:09.19,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:10.90,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:16.60,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.10,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.28,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.80,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,It's right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.26,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:35.81,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:36.91,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.18,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be reckless if it means I'll win...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:42.64,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,But if that always worked, \Nthis wouldn't be so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:45.48,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Orcbolg!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:47.86,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.48,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,All right... Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:54.07,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Beard-cutter. \NI'm putting my faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.74,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Things are indeed getting a bit difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:01.37,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,I see that the human girl has \Nused up all her miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:05.65,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Carbunculus... Crescunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.82,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Fear not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:15.88,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,If she manages to survive, I'll let her live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:19.08,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use her as either food or a plaything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.85,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,I need more goblins now, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.73,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Iacta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.02,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:07.89,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,What... What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:13.82,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,This is a gate scroll. I linked \Nit to the bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:15.93,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,The bottom of the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:17.82,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Then that was seawater?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:21.28,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,The water under the most \Npressure at the sea floor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:24.33,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,must've been swiftly unleashed, like a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:28.31,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,But to think it was a scroll \Nused for transfers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:31.11,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,It allows you to escape from \Nanywhere in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:33.89,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,It serves as a lifeline for adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:38.17,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,And yet he used it as a \Nlast resort in battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.43,Flashback,Witch,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:46.68,Flashback,Witch,0000,0000,0000,,he also asked a strange favor of \Nme once... that friend of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:52.29,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to use that \Nscroll to destroy a nest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.31,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,but this is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:58.83,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... What were you called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.70,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.30,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,Goblins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.91,Main,Ogre,0000,0000,0000,,You would use this to kill mere goblins?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:07.62,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Goblins...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.58,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,are far more troublesome than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:19.97,Main,Male elf,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:23.09,Main,Male elf,0000,0000,0000,,We received your letter and \Narrived as soon as we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:26.79,Main,Male elf,0000,0000,0000,,How many more goblins are insi—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:34.56,Main,Male elf,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, we're going to go scout inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:37.54,Main,Male elf,0000,0000,0000,,Please rest until you get to the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:43.56,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.37,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:48.45,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Does he always do stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.46,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:53.08,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,He's always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.91,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:59.55,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,But despite how it seems, \Nhe's quite aware of his surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:06.01,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't obligated to \Nteach me so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.18,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:12.16,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we should sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.02,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:27.70,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I still don't like Orcbolg.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:31.41,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, adventures are supposed to be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:36.99,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,The joy of experiencing the unknown \Nand discovering new things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:39.14,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling elated or accomplished...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:42.92,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my adventures are like.\NThis is no adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.76,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'll take you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.76,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,on an actual adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:35.15,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:41.25,sign_33927_268_Next_Time,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:41.25,sign_33927_269__Goblin_Slayer_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Adventures and Daily Life